                        sling:resourceType="core/franklin/components/block/v1/block/item"
                        model="text-container-text"
                        modelFields="[text]"
                        name="Text Container Text"
                        text="&lt;p>Since our inception in 2013, we’ve focused on taking on tough health challenges to make a real difference in people’s lives. In the past 10 years, we’ve invested over $50 billion to research, develop and discover new medicines and solutions. We’ve also expanded to over 50,000 employees who are focused every day on making a remarkable impact that lasts.&lt;br> &lt;br> While we have made great progress, it’s only the beginning. As we recognize a decade of impact, we turned to our employees around the globe to reflect on what motivates their work, how culture plays a part and what they see for the future of our company.&lt;/p>"/>
                </block_1>
                <block_2
                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
